{"tid":1975453,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"最近咁多人冇工番，有冇興趣學下外匯投資？","createTime":"2020-04-16T14:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T14:29:17.000Z","uid":353450,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"41cd146e0cfc042cc85ccfe85c18617981470bbb","tid":1975453,"uid":353450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:14:06.000Z","msg":"依家疫情嚴重，好多人失業，冇工番。<br />\n利用金融科技，只要一部手機，就可以係屋企輕鬆贏錢。<br />\n錢放係銀行，每年得個幾仙，點解唔令去投資呢？外匯入場門檻底，風險又可以自己管理，點解唔試下？<br />\n我係CK LTD international.🌐金融投資顧問<br />\nCK係馬來西亞有千人團隊，係最大外匯投資團隊，支援最多。<br />\n<br />\n想投資又唔識投資?成日聽人講投資資本要好多?到底點先開始到投資?唔識睇圖表?新手投資從何下手？點為之買賣？<br />\n<br />\n🏦人生總是&hellip;[想更好，卻怕改變]。但不改變，不可能會更好!<br />\n<br />\n我地設有買賣投資外匯模擬系統，利用假嘅金錢，讓你了解投資，建立投資信心。而且有投資課程，專家指導，還有投資Tips，教你買賣，讓你賺錢機會更大。💰<br />\nWhatsApp Me to know more.<br />\n其實香港好多人都挽緊外匯，佢唔會好似股市咁，一直跌。所以疫情時期，個個都轉曬挽外匯市場。<br />\n學多樣搵錢方法都無防。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wa.me/447383794720?text=What's%20up%20Xavier!%20I'm%20real%20interested%20in%20this%F0%9F%99%8C%F0%9F%8F%BB%F0%9F%93%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwa.me%2F447383794720%3Ftext%3DWhat%27s%2520up%2520Xavier%21%2520I%27m%2520real%2520interested%2520in%2520this%25F0%259F%2599%258C%25F0%259F%258F%25BB%25F0%259F%2593%2588&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10LZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=51b83bef\" target=\"_blank\">https://wa.me/447383794720?text=What's%20up%20Xavier!%20I'm%20real%20interested%20in%20this%F0%9F%99%8C%F0%9F%8F%BB%F0%9F%93%88</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eSxrzZZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeSxrzZZ.png&h=d2e42bb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da0ae59952f6defa43f325a847c0b1680e9f7fc4","tid":1975453,"uid":69022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:14:44.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"8239a6660501938046141bfa225eecb7f49851b7","tid":1975453,"uid":353450,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"da0ae59952f6defa43f325a847c0b1680e9f7fc4","tid":1975453,"uid":69022,"like":2